Quotes Scraper

This project is a simple Python web scraper that extracts quotes and their authors from the website quotes.toscrape.com and saves them into a CSV file.

ğŸ“Œ Features
Scrapes quotes and corresponding authors from the website's homepage.
Saves the extracted data into a structured quotes.csv file.
Uses requests, BeautifulSoup, and pandas for HTTP requests, HTML parsing, and data handling.

