ğŸš€ Getting Started
Make sure you have Python 3 installed along with the required libraries. You can install dependencies with:
		pip install requests beautifulsoup4 pandas
To run the scraper and generate the CSV file:
		python scraper.py
This will create a file called quotes.csv in your project directory containing all quotes and their authors from the first page of the website.

